{"commentv2": 1, "number": 7, "id": 693984, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "jfmartel", "body": "Having \"Projected Textures\" set at \"On\" in the video options for this fight REALLY helps. With this you can see where the ice is about to fall.", "date": "2009-04-25T22:07:03-05:00", "rating": 84, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "This is a musthave setting for alot of encounters. I find that some of my own abilities (desecration comes to mind) don't show up at all without this. Makes alot of fights that much easier.", "creationdate": "2009-04-28T23:33:03-05:00", "id": 94674, "rating": 15, "commentid": 693984, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "monoxide0184", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
