{"commentv2": 1, "number": 9, "id": 704960, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "360769", "body": "Healers bring tissues...this is really healing intense, unless the tank has some decent frost resist gear.", "date": "2009-05-04T09:22:44-05:00", "rating": 19, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Talking to my Shammy friend, not overly geared but well enough for Ulduar 10 and 25, he said that Hodir is a bit healing intensive but it can definitely be 2 healed. A LOT of the damage is avoidable, and if your DPS are retards it's gonna make it all that harder. One fight he did say, funnily enough, was Ignis was perhaps the hardest he's had to heal so far in Ulduar (his guild only has Mimiron, General and Yogg left on 25).", "creationdate": "2009-08-10T21:26:40-05:00", "id": 419776, "rating": 0, "commentid": 704960, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "nyctric", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 10, "id": 705752, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "358717", "body": "Mages could use Ice Block to unfreeze themsevles, if they got flash freezed.", "date": "2009-05-04T22:47:26-05:00", "rating": 55, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "My last post was just stating the irony of using a spell that freezes you to unfreeze yourself, Apparntly you downranking happy lug nuts thought I was serious  Cause video games are serious btw <_<  One again, sarcasm.", "creationdate": "2009-05-12T19:49:20-05:00", "id": 97579, "rating": 49, "commentid": 705752, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Skullhawk13", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
