{"commentv2": 1, "number": 66, "id": 3244591, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "akarisuicide", "body": "If you annoy him (i.e. click on him a lot), he says any of the following:\r\n[quote][b]Hodir![/b][/quote]\r\n[quote]I am Hodir.[/quote]\r\n[quote]I owe you one, but [i]don't[/i] push it.[/quote]\r\n[quote]Cool it.[/quote]\r\n[quote]Don't [i]make[/i] me have to put you on ice, small friend.[/quote]\r\n[quote]That's cold.[/quote]\r\n[quote]'s no big deal.[/quote]\r\n[quote]Stay frosty.[/quote]\r\nA [i]lot[/i] for one NPC!\r\n:3", "date": "2020-11-01T21:02:44-06:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
