{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 682125, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "lenpup", "body": "Champion of Hodir will periodically target the top threat player in the raid (after the MT) for a short period while he uses a cone of frost damage breath attack which roots the victims in it's damage cone in place and deals light damage for several seconds. You can have the 2nd highest threat person stand off his hip to get the cone aimed away from the rest of the group.\n\nBeware the \"Snow Mounds\" nearby this trash mob, proximity spawns a group of 5-10 \"Winter Jormungar\"  which will need to be AOE'd down.", "date": "2009-04-17T21:24:04-05:00", "rating": 6, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "The frost breath is random, not 2nd threat.", "creationdate": "2009-05-23T21:55:03-05:00", "id": 99725, "rating": 5, "commentid": 682125, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "297916", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2009-04-17T23:42:59-05:00", 2, "lenpup"]}
