{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 546997, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "Junyed", "body": "Are these part of a quest or something? Every time I fly by here I wonder why they're there, and why they're dead...", "date": "2009-01-04T19:40:51-06:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Same. I haven't seen anything regarding a quest, it may be a phased aspect or part of the whole conflict in the region between the Sons of Hodir, and Loken and his minions...", "creationdate": "2009-01-14T00:10:54-06:00", "id": 72575, "rating": 0, "commentid": 546997, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Aryn2382", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "They're there for the quest [url=http://www.wowhead.com/quest=12986]Fate of the Titans.[/url] You're sent to analyze the four temples, and you find that the servants are dead and the watchers missing, that's why the corpses are there.", "creationdate": "2010-09-10T12:12:40-05:00", "id": 181340, "rating": 1, "commentid": 546997, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "iMogwai", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 1, "id": 598941, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "296037", "body": "Actually these guys are dead because they were killed during Loken's attack on the temples of the titanic watchers.\r\nThe fate of Hodir himself is unknown, it is said that the Titanic watchers are deceased, although some speculate them to appear as raid bosses in the Ulduar raid.Perhaps as Undead bosses?\r\n\r\nP.S: Forgive my english. I`m just learning it.", "date": "2009-02-07T07:58:57-06:00", "rating": 15, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "No need dude, you speak english alot better then some people who are natural born.  Well. . . type english.  You know what i mean.", "creationdate": "2009-03-29T19:18:47-05:00", "id": 88343, "rating": 10, "commentid": 598941, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "173118", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 2, "id": 640659, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "shoobles", "body": "While I was working on http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=12986, I noticed that some of these servants can be a ridiculously low level. I encountered one that was level 9. Kind of odd for an NPC in a level 78+ zone.", "date": "2009-03-13T01:35:21-05:00", "rating": 6, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I saw a level 39 one. It seems you're right.", "creationdate": "2009-03-20T16:42:09-05:00", "id": 86589, "rating": 2, "commentid": 640659, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "296037", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "No wonder they're dead. :P", "creationdate": "2009-04-07T22:56:35-05:00", "id": 89967, "rating": 15, "commentid": 640659, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Arbron", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I saw one that was level 7, right next to one that was level 70. I'm guessing their levels are picked at random.", "creationdate": "2009-07-26T16:29:12-05:00", "id": 111950, "rating": 0, "commentid": 640659, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Bullfrogg", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 3, "id": 870898, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "jster", "body": "They seem to be there for decoration. I saw a level 8 next to an 80. They are in the temple of frost. Which would explain why they are servants of \"hodir\".\n\nHope this helps to clear things up.\n\nEdit: Also the Temple of Order has chains. Which could lead to further prove that they are just for decoration.", "date": "2009-10-19T17:26:39-05:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2009-10-19T17:29:20-05:00", 1, "jster"]}